c: 45
v: 23
t: "Umbonile na lowo uzithabathela iminqweno yakhe ayenze uthixo wakhe, uAllâh umyekele ekulahlekeni ngolwazi kwaye Ufake itywina ekuveni kwakhe nasentliziyweni yakhe, Waza Wabeka isigqumathelo phezu kokubona kwakhe? Ngubani ke onokumkhokela emva koAllâh? Ingaba aniyi kukhumbuzeka ke ngoko"